targets.rawSql:
SELECT $__timeInterval(time_local) AS time,
  count() AS requests
FROM "metrics"."cloudfront_logs"
WHERE ( time >= $__fromTime AND time <= $__toTime )
  AND ( domain = $domain )
AND ( bot IN ($bot) )
GROUP BY time
ORDER BY time ASC

SELECT $__timeInterval(time_local) AS time,
  toString(status) AS metric,
  count() AS value
FROM "metrics"."cloudfront_logs"
WHERE ( time >= $__fromTime AND time <= $__toTime )
  AND ( domain = $domain )
AND ( bot IN ($bot) )
GROUP BY time, status
ORDER BY time ASC

SELECT $__timeInterval(time_local) AS time,
  AVG(duration) AS metric
FROM "metrics"."cloudfront_logs"
WHERE ( time >= $__fromTime AND time <= $__toTime )
  AND ( domain = $domain )
AND ( bot IN ($bot) )
GROUP BY time
ORDER BY time ASC

SELECT  toString(toDate((intDiv(toUInt32(time_local), 86400) * 86400))) as date,
        CASE
            WHEN status = 200 THEN '200'
            WHEN status = 404 THEN '404'
            WHEN status = 400 THEN '400'
            WHEN status = 301 THEN '301'
            WHEN status >= 300 AND status < 400 THEN '3xx'
            WHEN status >= 400 AND status < 500 THEN '4xx'
            WHEN status >= 500 AND status < 600 THEN '5xx'
            ELSE 'Other'
        END AS status,
        count(*) as c
FROM    metrics.cloudfront_logs
WHERE   ( time_local >= $__fromTime AND time_local <= $__toTime )
    AND ( domain = $domain )
AND ( bot IN ($bot) )
GROUP BY date, status
ORDER BY date DESC, status

SELECT toString(date),
  `status`,
  method,
  url,
  COUNT(*) AS c
FROM metrics.cloudfront_logs
WHERE   ( time_local >= $__fromTime AND time_local <= $__toTime )
    AND ( domain = $domain )
AND ( bot IN ($bot) )
    AND `status` NOT IN (200, 201, 301)
    AND method != 'OPTIONS'
GROUP BY date, status, method, url
ORDER BY date DESC, c DESC
LIMIT 100

SELECT count(*) AS c
FROM metrics.cloudfront_logs
WHERE ( time_local >= $__fromTime AND time_local <= $__toTime )
  AND ( domain = $domain ) AND ( bot IN ($bot) )

SELECT COUNT(*) / ($__toTime - $__fromTime) c
FROM metrics.cloudfront_logs
WHERE ( time_local >= $__fromTime AND time_local <= $__toTime )
AND ( domain = $domain )
AND ( bot IN ($bot) )

AND ( bot IN ($bot) )

SELECT
  toString(toDate(toStartOfDay(time_local))) AS Date,
  COUNT(DISTINCT remote_addr) AS Visitors
FROM metrics.cloudfront_logs
WHERE ( time_local >= toStartOfMonth($__fromTime) AND time_local <= $__toTime )
-- ( time_local >= toStartOfMonth(current_timestamp()) AND time_local <= toLastDayOfMonth(current_timestamp()) )
  AND ( domain = $domain )
AND ( bot IN ($bot) )
GROUP BY Date
ORDER BY Date ASC
LIMIT 31

SELECT
  formatDateTime(time_local, '%W') AS DayOfWeek,
  formatDateTime(time_local, '%F') AS Date,
  COUNT(DISTINCT remote_addr) AS Visitors,
  COUNT() AS Requests,
  (Requests / Visitors) AS RequestsPerVisit,
  SUM(body_bytes_sent) AS Bandwidth,
  (Bandwidth / Visitors) As BandwidthPerVisit
FROM metrics.cloudfront_logs
WHERE ( time_local >= toStartOfMonth($__fromTime) AND time_local <= $__toTime )
-- ( time_local >= toStartOfMonth(current_timestamp()) AND time_local <= toLastDayOfMonth(current_timestamp()) )
  AND ( domain = $domain )
AND ( bot IN ($bot) )
GROUP BY Date, DayOfWeek
ORDER BY Date ASC
LIMIT 31
